title: NFL Around the League: July 24th, 2013
itunes:title: NFL Around the League: July 24th, 2013
description:
In the first episode of the new-and-improved Around the League podcast, Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal get you set for training camp with all the news from coast to coast. Plus, the guys wrap up their team-by-team previews with the NFC North and NFC East. Check out our newly-minted podcast and look for us soon on iTunes!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
